From cb54501db0e3c946471f360a75befa8a14ed59dc Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Arunpandi Kannan <arunpand@qti.qualcomm.com>
Date: Thu, 11 Sep 2025 00:30:51 +0530
Subject: [PATCH] QSDK:PROTOCOL:HOSTAPD: Support to provide hardcoded keypair
 in DPP  bootstrap

Add support to provide DPP private/public key pair through cli
command. Currently DPP generates keypair dynamcially each time.
This cli command will allow DPP to have consistent key pair all
the time, instead of negeration new key pair each reboot or loss
of key.

Usage:
DPP_BOOTSTRAP_SET_KEYPAIR privkey=<> pubkey=<> curve=<> mac=<> ...

Patch-dependency: None
Patch-work: None
Tag: DPP

Signed-off-by: Arunpandi Kannan <arunpand@qti.qualcomm.com>
